    whyItMatters: "Perpetual Adoration is one of the most powerful expressions of Catholic belief in the Real Presence. It provides a continuous stream of prayer, reparation, and intercession for the parish, the diocese, and the world, and offers individuals a place of profound encounter with Christ at any hour.",
