    whyItMatters: "The Mission Rosary expands the pray-er's horizons beyond personal needs to embrace the whole world. It cultivates missionary consciousness and reminds Catholics that every Rosary has universal power — each Hail Mary reaches the ends of the earth through the communion of saints.",
